TopicTitle: INner EXplorer 1 Mission, pushing IKSEP technology ever further.

Articles.Content:
I have just launched my first interplanetary mission! INEX-1 is a space probe that has gone to Eve to orbit it, I am so proud of the cute lil' thing!

-----------------------

Today, year 1 day 123, the INEX-1 beamed it's camera pictures of it's mission back to KSC Mission Control, after reviewing the files for any UFO's, the pictures were entered into the Public Archive Folder and released to all KerbalKind.
